12 Section 16. KRS 610.990 is amended to read as follows:
13 Any person who intentionally violates any of the provisions of this chapter shall be guilty
14 of a Class B misdemeanor[, except that an intentional violation of an order issued under
15 KRS 610.030(11) shall be referred to the county attorney for prosecution under KRS
